{"notes":[{"midi":0,"start":17.1,"dur":3.41,"lyric":"We were both young when I first saw you"},{"midi":0,"start":20.56,"dur":3.64,"lyric":"I close my eyes and the flashback starts"},{"midi":0,"start":24.26,"dur":3.33,"lyric":"I'm standin' there"},{"midi":0,"start":27.64,"dur":5.11,"lyric":"On a balcony in summer air"},{"midi":0,"start":33.05,"dur":3.97,"lyric":"See the lights, see the party, the ball gowns"},{"midi":0,"start":37.07,"dur":3.35,"lyric":"See you make your way through the crowd"},{"midi":0,"start":40.47,"dur":3.12,"lyric":"And say, \"Hello\""},{"midi":0,"start":43.64,"dur":4.9,"lyric":"Little did I know"},{"midi":0,"start":48.83,"dur":3.88,"lyric":"That you were Romeo, you were throwin' pebbles"},{"midi":0,"start":52.76,"dur":3.72,"lyric":"And my daddy said, \"Stay away from Juliet\""},{"midi":0,"start":56.53,"dur":2.58,"lyric":"And I was cryin' on the staircase"},{"midi":0,"start":59.16,"dur":5.55,"lyric":"Beggin' you, \"Please don't go, \" and I said"},{"midi":0,"start":65.01,"dur":4.16,"lyric":"Romeo, take me somewhere we can be alone"},{"midi":0,"start":69.22,"dur":4.14,"lyric":"I'll be waiting, all there's left to do is run"},{"midi":0,"start":73.41,"dur":3.78,"lyric":"You'll be the prince and I'll be the princess"},{"midi":0,"start":77.23,"dur":7.83,"lyric":"It's a love story, baby, just say, \"Yes\""},{"midi":0,"start":85.37,"dur":4.13,"lyric":"So I sneak out to the garden to see you"},{"midi":0,"start":89.54,"dur":3.15,"lyric":"We keep quiet, 'cause we're dead if they knew"},{"midi":0,"start":92.74,"dur":3.09,"lyric":"So close your eyes"},{"midi":0,"start":95.89,"dur":5.36,"lyric":"Escape this town for a little while, oh oh"},{"midi":0,"start":101.54,"dur":3.52,"lyric":"'Cause you were Romeo, I was a scarlet letter"},{"midi":0,"start":105.12,"dur":3.74,"lyric":"And my daddy said, \"Stay away from Juliet\""},{"midi":0,"start":108.91,"dur":2.16,"lyric":"But you were everything to me"},{"midi":0,"start":111.12,"dur":6.05,"lyric":"I was beggin' you, \"Please don't go, \" and I said"},{"midi":0,"start":117.47,"dur":4.18,"lyric":"Romeo, take me somewhere we can be alone"},{"midi":0,"start":121.7,"dur":3.99,"lyric":"I'll be waiting, all there's left to do is run"},{"midi":0,"start":125.73,"dur":4,"lyric":"You'll be the prince and I'll be the princess"},{"midi":0,"start":129.78,"dur":3.95,"lyric":"It's a love story, baby, just say, \"Yes\""},{"midi":0,"start":133.78,"dur":4.23,"lyric":"Romeo, save me, they're tryna tell me how to feel"},{"midi":0,"start":138.06,"dur":3.83,"lyric":"This love is difficult, but it's real"},{"midi":0,"start":141.94,"dur":3.94,"lyric":"Don't be afraid, we'll make it out of this mess"},{"midi":0,"start":145.92,"dur":19.13,"lyric":"It's a love story, baby, just say, \"Yes\""},{"midi":0,"start":165.28,"dur":3.91,"lyric":"I got tired of waiting"},{"midi":0,"start":169.24,"dur":3.77,"lyric":"Wonderin' if you were ever comin' around"},{"midi":0,"start":173.06,"dur":4.82,"lyric":"My faith in you was fading"},{"midi":0,"start":177.93,"dur":4.4,"lyric":"When I met you on the outskirts of town, and I said"},{"midi":0,"start":182.38,"dur":3.85,"lyric":"Romeo, save me, I've been feeling so alone"},{"midi":0,"start":186.28,"dur":3.88,"lyric":"I keep waiting for you, but you never come"},{"midi":0,"start":190.21,"dur":3.63,"lyric":"Is this in my head? I don't know what to think"},{"midi":0,"start":193.89,"dur":3.68,"lyric":"He knelt to the ground and pulled out a ring"},{"midi":0,"start":197.62,"dur":2.33,"lyric":"And said, \"Marry me, Juliet"},{"midi":0,"start":200,"dur":2.28,"lyric":"You'll never have to be alone"},{"midi":0,"start":202.33,"dur":3.8,"lyric":"I love you and that's all I really know"},{"midi":0,"start":206.19,"dur":4.04,"lyric":"I talked to your dad, go pick out a white dress"},{"midi":0,"start":210.27,"dur":7.84,"lyric":"It's a love story, baby, just say, \"Yes\""},{"midi":0,"start":218.41,"dur":3.31,"lyric":"Oh, oh, oh"},{"midi":0,"start":221.77,"dur":4.83,"lyric":"Oh, oh, oh, oh"